ed."],[5689,5889,"And why don't you do me a favor?"],[6297,6348,"And help me"],[6348,6468,"take it off."],[6802,6927,"You're such a tease."]],"25":[[8779,8917,"You're back, master."],[9346,9751,"So you must be Marco's new pet."]],"26":[[33,125,"Who are you?"],[229,446,"I should be asking you that."],[500,596,"And what are you"],[596,796,"doing in my husband's office?"],[809,925,"You're Mandy."],[930,1130,"You know me?"],[1155,1334,"Looks like Marco's really spoiling"],[1334,1422,"his new pet."],[1430,1497,"He said you two"],[1497,1697,"divorced a long time ago."],[1805,1989,"Well,"],[1997,2089,"Did Marco tell you I was"],[2089,2235,"his first sub?"],[2243,2331,"All the others he's had"],[2331,2427,"are just placeholders"],[2427,2619,"because he can't have me back."],[2627,2736,"Now get lost."],[2744,2944,"Marco asked me to wait here."],[2998,3148,"As the ex,"],[3157,3311,"you have no right to tell me"],[3311,3399,"to leave."],[3407,3653,"Oh, really?"],[3762,3858,"I guess you prefer"],[3858,4058,"the hard way."],[4120,4195,"Don't touch her!"],[4204,4341,"Marco!"],[4350,4504,"You're back."],[4512,4637,"I really missed you."],[4642,4721,"Did you miss me?"]],"27":[[37,120,"Don't touch her!"],[129,258,"Marco!"],[266,400,"You're back."],[429,513,"I really missed you."],[592,713,"Did you miss me?"],[734,888,"What are you doing here?"],[896,938,"I was just"],[938,1109,"giving your little pet a lesson."],[1163,1355,"Why are you so worked up?"],[1363,1564,"Leave your hands off her."],[1647,1760,"Come on."],[1768,1968,"She's just a sub."],[2077,2331,"Oh, I see."],[2473,2540,"You really fell"],[2540,2677,"for her, didn't you?"],[2798,2940,"I can't believe your taste"],[2940,3040,"has dropped so low"],[3040,3144,"since you left me."],[3186,3303,"That's none of your business."],[3311,3499,"Now get out of here and don't"],[3499,3653,"come back without my permission."],[4371,4454,"Did she hurt you?"],[4462,4662,"No, I didn't give her a chance."],[5000,5201,"Hey, look at me."],[5226