 roll your eyes"],[3636,3720,"at me?"],[3895,4049,"We're in Washington now."],[4058,4145,"You couldn't possibly"],[4145,4333,"punish me here, could you?"],[4341,4542,"Oh, I'm more than capable."],[4654,4825,"Take off your panties right now."]],"31":[[20,221,"Take off your panties right now."],[6790,6969,"Mr. Russo"],[6977,7094,"I'm so glad you"],[7094,7207,"could make it to my party."],[7211,7336,"My pleasure."],[7344,7545,"You remember my lady, Stephanie."],[7620,7770,"Nice to see you again."],[7778,7824,"Hi."],[7853,7978,"Hi, Flora. Nice to meet you."],[7978,8041,"Nice to meet you."],[8058,8312,"So, I heard that you purchased"],[8320,8433,"that piece of land"],[8433,8712,"out west for a hundred million."],[8767,8967,"You always know how to take the big"],[8975,9104,"bold risks."]],"32":[[8,150,"I just trust my instinct"],[150,346,"and I always get what I want."],[354,500,"Mr. Russo's business instinct"],[500,700,"is always spot on."],[888,1042,"So what do you"],[1042,1259,"plan to do with that land?"],[1368,1568,"I have a vision."],[1597,1743,"The moment I saw it,"],[1751,1851,"I knew it would"],[1851,1943,"become one of the"],[1943,2185,"most breathtaking places"],[2193,2394,"in the U.S.."],[3065,3119,"Excuse me."],[3119,3319,"I'll be right back."],[3611,3732,"You mentioned"],[3741,3899,"breathtaking."],[4617,4688,"Come on, Flora"],[4692,4850,"pull yourself together."],[5255,5384,"Okay."],[5847,5943,"No, no, mom."],[5943,6126,"Don't worry, okay?"],[6135,6235,"I'll make peace with dad"],[6235,6368,"in order to get his money."],[6702,6831,"Flora?"],[6902,7040,"What are you doing here?"]],"33":[[79,287,"Flora?"],[287,408,"What are you doing here?"],[479,771,"Shit. I can’t let Adam find me."],[867,980,"Flora, wait!"],[1242,1497,"Dammit! Get out of my way!"],[2339,2473,"That was close."],[2740,2911,"No! No, let me go!"]],"34":[[0,150,"No! Let me go!"],[154,325,"Hey, don't worry, it's me."],[496,575,"I thought you were inside"],[575,671,"talking business."],[713,759,"I was,"],[759,850,"but it took too long,"],[850,938,"so I had to come out"],[938,1063,"and find you."],[1368,1522,"Seriously?"],[1530,1697,"You can't even go one minute"],[1697,1897,"without me."],[1985,2043,"Did you just roll"],[2043,2206,"your eyes at me again?"],[2281,2352,"You've been such a"],[2352,2548,"naughty brat tonight."],[2585,2702,"I think it's time to show you"],[2702,2902,"the consequences."],[2940,3078,"What do you mean?"],[5947,6072,"Flora?"],[6239,6381,"We have to stop."],[6473,6673,"Then make me stop."],[7490,7628,"Flora, is that you?"]],"35":[[2369,2473,"Fuck!"],[2635,2736,"Hello?"],[2915,3053,"The deal went belly up."],[3286,3332,"Yeah."],[3340,3386,"Fine."],[3395,3516,"I'll be right there."],[4337,4512,"Don't do that to me again."],[4521,4658,"I promise."],[5038,5113,"Have you ever thought about"],[5113,5221,"making this public?"],[5643,5739,"You mean-"],[5747,5822,"I don't want to hide"],[5822,5976,"our relationship anymore."],[6060,6172,"I want everyone to know"],[6172,6277,"that you're mine."],[6531,6690,"I want that too but"],[6898,7098,"maybe not yet."],[7207,7374,"It's still too complicated."],[7382,7503,"It's okay."],[7511,7665,"We can take it slow."],[7845,7970,"You really want that?"],[8024,8208,"Of course I do."],[8216,8345,"I'm falling in love with you."]],"36":[[62,162,"I don't know."],[225,379,"Adam is my ex."],[387,533,"And he's your son."],[671,763,"Yeah."],[913,1076,"Every moment I spend with you"],[1080,1155,"feels like a sin."],[1155,1297,"I can't shake off,"],[1480,1593,"but"],[1705,1893,"I can live with that."],[1901,2056,"Can you?"],[2135,2335,"Yes, I can."],[2444,2686,"Because I'm falling for you, too."],[3983,4104,"Flora, wait!"],[4412,4500,"Damn it!"],[4508,4683,"So Flora,"],[4692,4775,"you think you can"],[4775,4975,"just cheat on me and walk away."],[5159,5355,"Once I finish my business,"],[5363,5563,"I'm coming for you."],[5584,5743,"You'll be mine."],[5751,5851,"Just wait and see."]],"37":[[179,287,"I'm sorry I got a little"],[287,487,"bit carried away last night."],[588,788,"I promise it won't happen again."],[821,921,"Don't worry about it."],[930,1051,"I'll fade soon."],[1105,1326,"I really should go"],[1334,1509,"before my mom starts worrying."],[1518,1630,"All right."],[1722,1851,"I'll see you later."],[2648,2748,"Mom."],[2756,2882,"Good morning."],[2927,3086,"Good morning."],[3132,3278,"Aren't you going to introduce us?"],[3332,3415,"Who’s this handsome"],[3415,3503,"young man?"],[3824,3983,"Just a..."],[4216,4275,"Oh my God."],[4275,4379,"Please tell me you are"],[4379,4454,"not dating him."],[4454,4521,"He looks old"],[4521,4688,"enough to be your father."],[4821,5025,"Hi Mrs. Wade, I’m Marco Russo."],[5034,5125,"I'm Flora’s -"],[5163,5242,"Marco and I"],[5242,5309,"Wait."],[5317,5522,"Mr. Russo, you look so familiar."],[5601,5801,"Have we met before?"],[5839,6039,"Does my mom recognize Marco?"],[6060,6214,"Does she know he is Adam's dad?"]],"38":[[75,196,"Yeah, yeah."],[204,404,"Mom, Marco"],[433,521,"comes to our"],[521,588,"bakery often,"],[588,629,"which is why"],[629,829,"he probably looks so familiar."],[913,1013,"Marco?"],[1076,1167,"Uh that-"],[1167,1267,"That's right."],[1530,1730,"Well, if he's only a customer,"],[1751,1818,"then why is he"],[1818,2010,"giving you a ride home after"],[2018,2218,"you stayed out all night?"],[2306,2427,"It's just a coincidence."],[2427,2565,"I met Marco at the party"],[2573,2802,"which went late, so he offered to"],[2811,3011,"give me a ride home."],[3153,3261,"Okay."],[3269,3411,"Well,"],[3420,3591,"thank you, Mr. Russo."],[3657,3787,"You're welcome."],[3795,4054,"Since Flora’s safe, I"],[4158,4329,"shall be going."],[6156,6356,"Something doesn't feel right."],[6402,6523,"What's going on?"],[6523,6773,"Nothing mom. I’m just really tired."],[6881,7027,"Then how do you explain that"],[7027,7228,"bruise on your arm?"],[7236,7432,"Don't say it was an accident."],[7453,7595,"Did Mr. Russo hurt you?"],[7595,7636,"No, mom."],[7645,7757,